ity B&amp;O rates are never quoted as a fixed percentage and are confirmed against the Department of Revenue source before charging. TechBrot provides bookkeeping and QuickBooks work and coordinates with your CPA, EA, and the Washington Department of Revenue; we do not file Washington returns, the B&amp;O / Combined Excise Tax Return, the sales-tax return, the capital-gains tax, or any city B&amp;O return, and do not represent clients before tax authorities.</p>
